#: src/administration/on_aws.md:1
msgid "Install on AWS"
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/on_aws.md:3
msgid ""
"⚠️ **Disclaimer:** this installation method is not recommended by the Lemmy "
"developers. If you have any problems, you need to solve them yourself or ask "
"the respective authors. If you notice any Lemmy bugs on an instance "
"installed like this, please mention it in the bug report."
msgstr ""

